label: ACCOUNTNUMBER
description: This field stores the linked share account number.

label: ID
description: This field stores the ID of the linked share.

label: COMMENT1
description: This field stores 40 characters of comment information.

label: RECORDCHANGEDATE
description: The system stores the system date in this field when you create, change, or save the Share Analysis Group record.

label: LOCATOR
description: The system automatically assigns the Locator value when the record is created, and it cannot be changed.
